MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This Mapping fetches the data from LAWSON database POVAGRMTLN table and loads the data into MAKE_HOLD_LINE table of TPROD1
MAPPING.NAME: m_MAKE_HOLD_LINE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Fetches reqired columns values and have generic filter conditions in sql override.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_POVAGRMTLN

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT POVAGRMTLN.PROCURE_GROUP, POVAGRMTLN.VEN_AGRMT_REF, POVAGRMTLN.LINE_NBR, POVAGRMTLN.PURCH_FR_LOC, POVAGRMTLN.ITEM, POVAGRMTLN.UOM, POVAGRMTLN.HOLD_FLAG, POVAGRMTLN.AGRMT_MAX_QTY, POVAGRMTLN.ORDER_MIN_QTY, POVAGRMTLN.QTY_ORDERED, POVAGRMTLN.EFFECTIVE_DT, POVAGRMTLN.EXPIRE_DT, POVAGRMTLN.R_STATUS FROM $$SCHEMA.POVAGRMTLN, $$SCHEMA.POVAGRMTHD WHERE POVAGRMTLN.PROCURE_GROUP = POVAGRMTHD.PROCURE_GROUP AND POVAGRMTLN.VEN_AGRMT_REF = POVAGRMTHD.VEN_AGRMT_REF AND POVAGRMTHD.AGMT_TYPE = 'B' AND POVAGRMTHD.CLOSE_COMMIT_F <> 1 AND POVAGRMTHD.R_STATUS<> 3 AND POVAGRMTHD.EXPIRE_DT>SYSDATE AND POVAGRMTLN.AGMT_TYPE = 'B' AND POVAGRMTLN.R_STATUS<> 3 AND POVAGRMTLN.EXPIRE_DT>SYSDATE AND ( POVAGRMTHD.VEN_AGRMT_REF like 'MH%' or POVAGRMTHD.VEN_AGRMT_REF like 'BH%' )
